rows.label: tlk4130009102_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, thanks for visiting!
Thank you for telling us
what her parents said.

rows.label: tlk4130009102_msg0002
rows.name:
Riana's father wouldn't even
speak to me at first, but
her mother helped out.

rows.label: tlk4130009102_msg0003
rows.name:
She said that if we can be happy
together, it might change the
relationship between Gula and Superbia.

rows.label: tlk4130009102_msg0004
rows.name:
After that, we had a long talk, and
he finally approved of our marriage!
It's all thanks to you guys.
